        | SpriteBreaker is an open source web based sprite management tool build by 
        a(href="" style="white-space:nowrap") Wilfred Godfrey
        |. SpriteBreaker aims to make managing and updating spritesheets as simple as possible.

        h4 Quick start guide
        ol
          li Load an image using the file selector
          li Add and name a new sprite 
            code eg "mario"
          li Add and name a new action 
            code eg "stand"
          li Add a new frame
          li Set frame coordinates
          li Repeat
        ul
          li Scroll and click on the small canvas to set the view area
          li Left click on the large canvas to set the top left frame coordinate
          li Right click on the large canvas to set the bottom right frame coordinate
          li Scroll on the large canvas to zoom in and out
        ul
